CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 13, 1960, pg. 28 reads: "Jones and the Mrs. - San Francisco Giants' pitcher, Sam Jones, and his wife, Mary, had a chance to renew Pittsburgh friendships over the week-end when they visited here for the dapper Dan banquet. Jones was one of three tan athletes honored at the fete. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of San Francisco Giants pitcher Sam Jones and his wife Mary Jones, posed in interior with table and lamp
